snippet.title: Noelle Does Her Best! - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Tired of living in the countryside and desperate to move out, Noelle decides to purchase a house that was suspiciously cheap. Now trapped in crippling debt, Noelle has to do her best and take on as many jobs as possible to pay it off! To her dismay, her troubles only worsen after she pays off the hefty debt.
